longBusinessSummary: Prabha Energy Limited engages in conventional and unconventional oil and gas exploration, production, and trading in India. The company's portfolio encompasses onshore exploration and production assets in both conventional and unconventional hydrocarbons. It also has a participating interest in two coal bed methane (CBM) blocks, including North Karanpura CBM block and Jharia CBM block-1. Prabha Energy Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Ahmedabad, India.
